<!--index.wxml-->
<view class="pt-20 pb-20 pr-20 pl-20">
  <image class="width-100 glass-banner" mode="aspectFit" src="../../images/glass/topbanner.jpg"></image>
  <view class="glass-tit">
    配镜流程
  </view>
  <view class="bg-fff width-100 pt-20">
    <view class="glass-tit-bar  color-fff text-center bg-blue">
      预约到店
    </view>
    <view class="pb-20 break-word text-center pb-20">预约到店 — 专业验光师为您验光 — 挑选喜欢的镜架 —
      根据度数验光师提供专业选镜片建议 — 购买付款</view>
  </view>
  <view class="glass-tit">
    配镜知识点
  </view>
  <view class="bg-fff width-100 pt-20">
    <view class="glass-tit-bar  color-fff text-center bg-blue">
      根据不同的度数选择适配镜片
    </view>
    <view class="pb-20 break-word text-center">0-400 度 — 1.56 镜片（1.551/1.552/1.553/1.561）
      400-600 度 — 1.61 镜片（1.592/1.599/1.600/1.601）
      600-800 度 — 1.67 镜片（1.661/1.665/1.670）
      800 度+ — 1.74 镜片（1.737）
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="bg-fff width-100 pt-20 mt-40">
    <view class="glass-tit-bar  color-fff text-center bg-blue">
      球面镜片与非球面镜片的区别
    </view>
    <view class="break-word text-center">
      下图均为眼镜片原片侧面示意图
    </view>
    <view class="flex-box-around pb-20">
      <view class="break-word text-center ">
        <image class="glass-item-img" src="../../images/glass/feiqiu.png"></image>非球面镜片<view>比较薄、美观、看物不易变形</view>
      </view>
      <view class="break-word text-center">
        <image class="glass-item-img" src="../../images/glass/qiu.png"></image>球面镜片
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="bg-fff width-100 pt-20 mt-40">
    <view class="glass-tit-bar  color-fff text-center bg-blue">
      影响加工后成品镜片厚薄的因素
    </view>
    <view class="break-word text-center glass-tit-text">
      1. 眼镜框的大小影响厚薄
    </view>
    <view class="flex-box-around ">
      <view class="break-word text-center">
        <image class="glass-item-img-h" src="../../images/glass/hou.png"></image>镜框大，镜片边缘显厚
      </view>
      <view class="break-word text-center">
        <image class="glass-item-img-b mb-40" src="../../images/glass/bo.png"></image>镜框小，镜片边缘显薄
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="break-word text-center glass-tit-text">
      2. 度数的大小影响厚薄，同为1.61折射率镜片
    </view>
    <view class="flex-box-around pb-20">
      <view class="break-word text-center">
        <image class="glass-item-img" src="../../images/glass/600.png"></image>600度
      </view>
      <view class="break-word text-center">
        <image class="glass-item-img" src="../../images/glass/400.png"></image>400度
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="break-word text-center">
      度数越低，镜片越薄
    </view>
    <view class="break-word text-center glass-tit-text">
      3. 折射率的大小影响厚薄，同为600度近视
    </view>
    <view class="flex-box-around ">
      <view class="break-word text-center">
        <image class="glass-item-img" src="../../images/glass/600.png"></image>1.61
      </view>
      <view class="break-word text-center">
        <image class="glass-item-img" src="../../images/glass/400.png"></image>1.67
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="break-word text-center glass-tit-text">
      折射率越高，镜片越薄
    </view>
  </view>
</view>